- Display drivers
  - In-memory bitmap
    - That can then be used with eglib_DrawBitmap for artifact free updates.
  - SDL (simulator)
  - SSD1306 (OLED) https://cdn-shop.adafruit.com/datasheets/SSD1306.pdf
